<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script type="text/javascript" charset="UTF-8"  src="/views/home/register.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/home/styles.css" type="text/css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nfHeader">
        <a href="/" class="svg-nflogo">
            <svg></svg>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="Container">
        <div class="centerConatiner">
            <form method="POST">
                <div class="registerFormContainer">
                    <div>
                        <div class="stepHeader-Container">
                            <div class="stepHeader">
                                <span>
                                    1/3 단계
                                </span>
                                <h1>회원님, 반갑습니다. 넷플릭스 가입절차는 간단합니다.</h1>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contextRow">몇 단계만 더 거치면 넷플릭스 가입 완료!<br>복잡한 단</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li class="nfFormSpace">
                                <div>
                                    <input class="nfTextField" type="email" placeholder="이메일 주소">

                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nfFormSpace">
                                <div>
                                    <input class="nfTextField" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 추가하세요">
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nfFormSpace">
                                <div>
                                    <input type="checkbox">
                                    <label>예, 저는 개인정보 처리방침에 따른 개인정보 수집 및 활용에 동의합니다.</label>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nfFormSpace">
                                <div>
                                    <input type="checkbox">
                                    <label>예, 넷플릭스 특별 할인 알림 이메일을 보내주세요. (선택 사항)</label>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="submitBtn">
                        <button type="submit">동의하고 계속</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>


</body>